110
00:07:29,489 --> 00:07:31,619
Right. Everyone must be there, right?

111
00:07:31,619 --> 00:07:32,660
"Everyone"?

112
00:07:35,359 --> 00:07:38,600
- I guess you have plans.
- Yes.

113
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:42,530
- With whom?
- Someone.

114
00:07:45,070 --> 00:07:46,869
Of course, it is someone.

115
00:07:47,369 --> 00:07:50,210
