133
00:08:36,989 --> 00:08:38,290
We share the same interests.

134
00:08:40,659 --> 00:08:41,729
"We"?

135
00:08:41,729 --> 00:08:43,529
I'll leave you alone so that you can
enjoy the book for your hormones.

136
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:44,560
