147
00:09:19,659 --> 00:09:21,430
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Quickly.

148
00:09:23,029 --> 00:09:24,899
Do not walk backwards. Turn
around and walk out quickly.

149
00:09:24,899 --> 00:09:25,970
Hurry up.

150
00:09:26,739 --> 00:09:28,409
What is it that you are taking so long?

151
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:30,409
Please be honest with me.

152
00:09:35,050 --> 00:09:36,180
It depends on the question.

153
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:38,080
I will not say it if you
are not going to be honest.

154
00:09:38,649 --> 00:09:39,649
Forget it, then.

155
00:09:39,779 --> 00:09:40,989
Among men!

156
00:09:40,989 --> 00:09:44,220
Among men, who do you cherish the most?

157
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:54,729
Jang Bong Hwan.

158
00:09:55,930 --> 00:09:57,540
And who might that be?

159
00:09:57,540 --> 00:10:00,070
He is...

160
00:10:01,509 --> 00:10:04,139
the only man in the world who is perfect.

161
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:07,279
He's the coolest guy I know.

162
00:10:07,479 --> 00:10:10,080
He's got everything.

163
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,979
He's got looks, a great personality,

164
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:13,680
incredible skills with a blade,

165
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:15,989
and a mastery of all theories,
which makes him the ultimate man.

166
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:18,820
He's the best.

167
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,519
He always feels new. He makes me thrilled!

168
00:10:21,659 --> 00:10:24,259
