181
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,999
Yes. I am jealous.

182
00:11:01,869 --> 00:11:03,830
You are not public property.

183
00:11:04,029 --> 00:11:07,300
So do not say "we" carelessly.

184
00:11:08,470 --> 00:11:09,540
That is an order.

185
00:11:10,509 --> 00:11:11,639
I do not want anyone else...

186
00:11:11,879 --> 00:11:14,979
