No. Stop it, Kim So Yong.

204
00:12:51,509 --> 00:12:54,040
Stop it. Stop it already.

205
00:12:55,310 --> 00:12:57,779
Does this upset you that much?

206
00:12:58,479 --> 00:13:01,619
