gentle elders in the palace.

212
00:13:52,100 --> 00:13:55,139
In the palace, everyone has secrets.

213
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,879
Let us unveil...

214
00:13:57,879 --> 00:13:59,840
the secrets that seem
too trivial to reveal...

215
00:14:00,180 --> 00:14:04,779
but provoke too much curiosity to ignore.

