218
00:14:29,769 --> 00:14:31,509
KIM JWA GEUN

219
00:14:31,609 --> 00:14:33,509
KIM MUN GEUN

220
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:43,420
It would be perfect if
I get a tiger card now.

221
00:14:44,989 --> 00:14:47,489
