of the dragon in the sky.

228
00:15:03,970 --> 00:15:06,609
He needs the dragon card.

229
00:15:14,519 --> 00:15:17,149
Whichever it is, I am doomed.

230
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:20,060
What are you doing? Play your hand.

231
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:22,460
Where did the tujeon player go?

232
00:15:23,729 --> 00:15:25,200
Actually,

233
00:15:25,659 --> 00:15:27,869
because the game is so interesting,

234
00:15:28,330 --> 00:15:31,239
