256
00:16:48,310 --> 00:16:49,409
I do not know about that.

257
00:16:49,409 --> 00:16:52,680
All I remember is serving you.

258
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:55,920
Calm down. Please do not fight.

259
00:16:56,090 --> 00:16:59,489
Blood is thicker than these mere cards.

260
00:17:04,330 --> 00:17:06,530
Ever since we were young,
every time we played,

261
00:17:06,530 --> 00:17:09,129
we would always growl at each other.

262
00:17:09,699 --> 00:17:12,169
We are very competitive.

263
00:17:12,169 --> 00:17:13,469
That is right.

264
00:17:14,070 --> 00:17:16,209
No matter how old we get,

265
00:17:16,209 --> 00:17:19,139
I am just a child before you.

266
00:17:20,179 --> 00:17:23,250
I will make a concession. You should take it.

267
00:17:23,250 --> 00:17:26,050
No, you should take this first.

268
00:17:26,050 --> 00:17:28,389
- Brother.
- Sister.

269
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:31,560
My goodness. Look at you.

270
00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:33,859
You are both competitive...

271
00:17:33,859 --> 00:17:36,429
and yet you both make
concessions so generously.

272
00:17:36,429 --> 00:17:40,429
Anyone can tell that you are
siblings. You are so alike.

273
00:17:41,060 --> 00:17:42,570
- That is not true!
- That is not true!

274
00:17:49,510 --> 00:17:52,810
Then, for the sake of your relationship,

275
00:17:52,810 --> 00:17:54,510
let us say that I won this round.

276
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:56,010
- What are you talking about?
- What are you talking about?

277
00:18:03,590 --> 00:18:04,889
I want to go home.

278
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,399
From the southeastern sky,

279
00:18:14,399 --> 00:18:17,030
there is a red energy
shooting towards the palace.

280
00:18:17,270 --> 00:18:19,270
It is as strong as fire.

281
00:18:19,869 --> 00:18:22,270
The river flows backwards.

282
00:18:22,270 --> 00:18:24,369
Frogs rain down from the sky.

283
00:18:24,580 --> 00:18:27,179
A series of strange events are occurring.

284
00:18:27,439 --> 00:18:29,649
Everyone is confused and worried...

285
00:18:29,850 --> 00:18:32,020
about such inauspicious signs.

286
00:18:32,649 --> 00:18:34,179
Word among the people is that...

287
00:18:34,419 --> 00:18:38,189
it is a sign of the end
of the world drawing near.

288
00:18:38,459 --> 00:18:39,490
I am worried.

289
00:18:43,889 --> 00:18:44,959
Is...

290
00:18:47,500 --> 00:18:50,199
the world really coming to an end?

291
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:01,679
THE SECRET OF DESTRUCTION

292
00:19:19,159 --> 00:19:20,359
Tonight,

293
00:19:21,830 --> 00:19:24,129
the sky will fall.

294
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:28,340
Fire will fall from the sky,

295
00:19:29,109 --> 00:19:33,780
and everything will burn.

296
00:19:35,250 --> 00:19:39,719
It will turn into a blazing inferno.

297
00:19:40,679 --> 00:19:42,050
Maybe the world...

298
00:19:42,449 --> 00:19:44,889
has always been ready to be destroyed.

299
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:48,730
It is not strange even if the world
comes to an end at any moment.

300
00:19:49,490 --> 00:19:53,500
If you had that so, you should have told us.

301
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:56,330
If I had known, I would
not have worked so hard.

302
00:19:56,570 --> 00:19:58,969
I would have enjoyed my life at ease.

303
00:19:59,199 --> 00:20:01,369
This darned world.

304
00:20:02,709 --> 00:20:04,109
I do not think...

305
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:08,609
the world will come to an end so easily.

306
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:11,179
Even small creatures like us...

307
00:20:11,179 --> 00:20:13,179
struggle to survive.

308
00:20:14,020 --> 00:20:16,189
The world would not be that weak.

309
00:20:17,520 --> 00:20:20,419
So let us stop thinking about it,

310
00:20:20,419 --> 00:20:23,459
and focus on finishing the book on tactics.

311
00:20:23,459 --> 00:20:24,530
Yes, Your Majesty.

312
00:20:24,929 --> 00:20:26,500
Bring the brush and ink.

313
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:28,770
You are going to squeeze me out to the end?

314
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:30,070
I am not doing this.

315
00:20:31,199 --> 00:20:32,300
Special Director Hong.

316
00:20:32,399 --> 00:20:36,369
What if this really is
the last day of my life?

317
00:20:36,369 --> 00:20:38,540
I do not want to die working to the end.

318
00:20:38,540 --> 00:20:41,980
You should consider today as your last day,

319
00:20:41,980 --> 00:20:43,780
and do what you want.

320
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:46,080
That is why I want to
finish creating this book.

321
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:48,990
It is something I want
to finish before I die.

322
00:20:48,990 --> 00:20:51,320
You are a fool who is obsessed with work.

323
00:20:51,619 --> 00:20:54,619
You need to watch your mouth.

324
00:20:54,619 --> 00:20:55,760
What do you care?

325
00:20:56,090 --> 00:20:58,129
It all ends once the world comes to an end.

326
00:20:58,659 --> 00:21:00,959
Did you just talk informally to me?

327
00:21:00,959 --> 00:21:03,000
Yes. Yes, I did.

328
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:04,199
We are all about to die.

329
00:21:04,199 --> 00:21:05,369
I cannot afford to be polite.

330
00:21:05,369 --> 00:21:07,139
Calm down, Special Director Hong.

331
00:21:07,139 --> 00:21:09,369
Won Beom, you punk. You are the worst.

332
00:21:09,369 --> 00:21:11,909
You are a corrupt employer
pretending to be my friend.

333
00:21:12,679 --> 00:21:16,209
Your Majesty. I too must do
something on my last day of life.

334
00:21:18,010 --> 00:21:19,780
Even if this day is my last,

335
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:22,050
I will fix your manners for you before I die.

336
00:21:23,449 --> 00:21:26,689
Gosh. You are so authoritative
just because you are a bit older.

337
00:21:27,419 --> 00:21:29,830
Plus, did you have to be that tall?

338
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:32,199
Did you eat all the
potatoes on Ganghwa Island?

339
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:35,770
That is cold.

340
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:39,070
I finally came to my senses.

341
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:40,800
I will stop right there.

342
00:21:48,179 --> 00:21:49,209
It is 5pm.

343
00:21:49,649 --> 00:21:51,050
It will soon be nightfall.

344
00:21:51,050 --> 00:21:52,520
Is today really the last day?

345
00:21:57,020 --> 00:21:58,159
Where are you going?

346
00:21:58,159 --> 00:21:59,590
I have changed my mind.

347
00:22:01,419 --> 00:22:04,689
If the world ends tonight,

348
00:22:04,689 --> 00:22:06,129
where I should be...

349
00:22:06,699 --> 00:22:09,030
and with whom I should be
not to have any regrets.

350
00:22:13,869 --> 00:22:16,310
It's fine. Don't worry.

351
00:22:18,139 --> 00:22:21,409
I said it's fine. Nothing's going to happen.

352
00:22:22,209 --> 00:22:23,850
Still, there are rumors.

353
00:22:23,850 --> 00:22:25,350
Don't trust the rumors.

354
00:22:25,350 --> 00:22:27,449
It's fine. It's all right.

355
00:22:27,679 --> 00:22:31,219
It's okay. My goodness. I said it's fine.

356
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:34,219
Don't trust those rumors.

357
00:22:34,830 --> 00:22:36,659
His Majesty is here.

358
00:22:43,429 --> 00:22:46,270
Are you also unable to sleep...

359
00:22:46,270 --> 00:22:48,000
in fear of the world coming to an end?

360
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:49,639
Come to an end, my foot.

361
00:22:49,939 --> 00:22:52,580
I was comforting them
because they were so worried.

362
00:22:52,909 --> 00:22:56,149
I can't ignore the woes of women.

363
00:22:56,810 --> 00:22:57,879
How kind of you.

364
00:22:58,949 --> 00:23:00,949
Hey. Royal Chef.

365
00:23:01,790 --> 00:23:03,619
What are you still doing here at this hour?

366
00:23:07,560 --> 00:23:08,830
Your Highness.

367
00:23:15,830 --> 00:23:16,869
What?

368
00:23:19,939 --> 00:23:21,340
Is something good going on?

369
00:23:26,209 --> 00:23:29,949
Are you that scared of dying, Man Bok?

370
00:23:29,949 --> 00:23:32,280
I was scared. What?

371
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:35,449
My eyes were just tearing
up from chopping scallions.

372
00:23:35,649 --> 00:23:38,020
Is that so? Sure, sure.

373
00:23:38,020 --> 00:23:39,459
My goodness.

374
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:42,830
I have always been in on
such important rumors.

375
00:23:42,990 --> 00:23:45,760
How come I was not aware
of the end of the world?

376
00:23:47,359 --> 00:23:51,230
Anyway, it is getting late.

377
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:04,149
Gosh, it's cold.

378
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:07,050
See? I told you. Nothing's happening.

379
00:24:07,050 --> 00:24:08,790
You all had me scared. Let's go.

380
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:10,850
- Let's go.
- The Queen is right.

381
00:24:11,959 --> 00:24:15,189
You should stop worrying and go to bed.

382
00:24:15,459 --> 00:24:16,689
Yes, Your Majesty.

383
00:24:16,929 --> 00:24:17,959
Hurry up.

384
00:24:18,560 --> 00:24:21,830
Your Highness. Is that...

385
00:24:35,750 --> 00:24:36,980
A meteor shower.

386
00:24:38,750 --> 00:24:39,879
A meteor shower.

387
00:24:40,250 --> 00:24:41,990
Is that rain?

388
00:24:46,060 --> 00:24:49,030
How is it that the end of
the world is so beautiful?

389
00:25:01,469 --> 00:25:04,169
Please let me go back to my healthy body.

390
00:25:04,369 --> 00:25:06,179
While I'm lying in bed in a coma,

391
00:25:06,179 --> 00:25:08,409
please don't let me lose muscle mass.

392
00:25:09,310 --> 00:25:10,310
My Queen.

393
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:16,520
If you see a shooting star,
make a wish and it'll come true.

394
00:25:16,520 --> 00:25:18,149
Make a wish. Hurry.

395
00:25:19,719 --> 00:25:20,719
Make a wish.

396
00:25:20,719 --> 00:25:22,730
A wish?

397
00:25:29,570 --> 00:25:33,070
Let Cheoljong live longer than
what the history books say...

398
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:35,139
and live happily ever after...

399
00:25:35,770 --> 00:25:37,510
like a prince in a fairy tale.

400
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:43,080
Please let me be born as a stone...

401
00:25:43,280 --> 00:25:45,649
in my next life.

402
00:25:48,149 --> 00:25:49,719
Why do you want to be a stone?

403
00:25:50,189 --> 00:25:52,490
So I will not have to do
anything and live comfortably.

404
00:25:55,090 --> 00:25:56,959
Then in my next life,

405
00:25:56,959 --> 00:25:59,260
I will kick that stone.

406
00:26:07,869 --> 00:26:09,310
In my next life,

407
00:26:09,310 --> 00:26:12,310
let me be born as Her Highness' mother.

408
00:26:12,679 --> 00:26:14,510
Please let me succeed...

409
00:26:14,510 --> 00:26:17,149
in rehabilitating Her
Majesty in my next life.

410
00:26:17,810 --> 00:26:21,080
In my next life, let me be born
as Her Highness' elder sister.

411
00:26:21,820 --> 00:26:23,520
So she would not be lonely.

412
00:26:25,189 --> 00:26:26,689
It was a good life.

413
00:26:27,359 --> 00:26:30,760
I hope my next life is as good as this life.

414
00:26:33,300 --> 00:26:34,330
If...

415
00:26:34,929 --> 00:26:37,300
I am ever reborn in my next life...

416
00:26:43,639 --> 00:26:45,139
I told you to make a wish,

417
00:26:45,139 --> 00:26:47,209
but it seems you're all
wishing to be born again.

418
00:26:47,409 --> 00:26:49,350
What did you wish to be born as?

419
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:50,850
No matter how much I think about it,

420
00:26:52,020 --> 00:26:54,320
I do not want to be born again.

421
00:26:56,189 --> 00:26:57,189
No wonder.

422
00:26:57,850 --> 00:27:00,020
If you pour so much into this life,

423
00:27:00,020 --> 00:27:01,929
you wouldn't want to be born again.

424
00:27:03,629 --> 00:27:05,060
It's okay even if it's hard.

425
00:27:05,399 --> 00:27:07,100
I know you're trying hard.

426
00:27:07,899 --> 00:27:10,100
I know you're trying so hard not to crumble.

427
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:17,439
Still, I want you to be reborn.

428
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:20,980
I've learned something
from living a second life.

429
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:24,409
Trivial things that I
would probably regret...

430
00:27:24,409 --> 00:27:25,580
if I hadn't known about them.

431
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:29,449
Right. I would have regretted it so much...

432
00:27:30,050 --> 00:27:33,159
if my life ended without meeting...

433
00:27:33,490 --> 00:27:34,919
such a strange person like you.

434
00:27:35,689 --> 00:27:36,730
Who knows?

435
00:27:36,730 --> 00:27:39,330
I might show up before you in an
unexpected and strange form...

436
00:27:39,330 --> 00:27:40,560
once again.

437
00:27:41,560 --> 00:27:44,000
So you have to be reborn.

438
00:27:46,300 --> 00:27:48,869
You are already unexpected enough even now.

439
00:27:58,820 --> 00:28:02,389
My family died on the same day.

440
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:07,760
I hope to meet them again in the afterlife.

441
00:28:24,340 --> 00:28:25,580
Are you okay?

442
00:28:29,050 --> 00:28:31,050
Did you make a wish?

443
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:35,080
There is one more wish.

444
00:28:36,149 --> 00:28:37,990
I know it cannot happen now,

445
00:28:40,189 --> 00:28:41,689
but one day,

446
00:28:44,359 --> 00:28:46,100
I want to...

447
00:28:48,260 --> 00:28:51,070
watch the sun setting in the distance...

448
00:28:51,969 --> 00:28:53,840
with the person I long for.

449
00:29:07,419 --> 00:29:10,990
How nice it would have been
for her to be here as well.

450
00:29:42,649 --> 00:29:43,889
What's with this mood?

451
00:29:47,490 --> 00:29:48,790
No in-house romance.

452
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:50,330
You cannot date your family.

453
00:29:50,330 --> 00:29:52,929
That is not what I meant.

454
00:29:52,929 --> 00:29:56,629
I am a man of much guilt.

455
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:02,939
I am a woman of much guilt.

456
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:08,340
I said, no in-house romance.

457
00:30:14,619 --> 00:30:18,020
When I am born again, I
hope to meet My Queen again.

458
00:30:18,689 --> 00:30:21,119
Even if we misunderstand,
hate each other and fight,

459
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:23,629
I hope we recognize each other in the end.

460
00:30:24,189 --> 00:30:25,730
I hope we meet again not as King and Queen,

461
00:30:26,129 --> 00:30:28,730
but as So Yong and Won Beom.

462
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:35,639
Everyone. Dismissed.

463
00:30:36,109 --> 00:30:37,469
Dismissed.

464
00:30:37,469 --> 00:30:40,280
Your Highness. The flames
are falling this way.

465
00:30:40,280 --> 00:30:43,149
Your Highness. Maybe
there is a fire somewhere.

466
00:30:43,310 --> 00:30:44,350
We are doomed.

467
00:30:45,580 --> 00:30:47,219
- We are totally doomed.
- Fire.

468
00:30:47,879 --> 00:30:50,250
We're not doomed.

469
00:30:50,250 --> 00:30:52,659
Wish for it a million
times. It will never happen.

470
00:30:52,959 --> 00:30:56,330
Look. It may be a mess,
but it's running fine.

471
00:30:56,560 --> 00:30:57,760
Seriously.

472
00:30:58,389 --> 00:31:00,929
This darned world is darn strong.

473
00:31:01,330 --> 00:31:05,270
It is a darned world, but it never ends.

474
00:31:10,340 --> 00:31:11,369
Oh, dear.

475
00:31:37,070 --> 00:31:38,669
MR. QUEEN: THE SECRET

476
00:31:38,669 --> 00:31:39,870
THIS DRAMA IS FICTIONAL AND
ALL CHARACTERS, ORGANIZATIONS,

477
00:31:39,870 --> 00:31:40,676
AND EVENTS ARE UNRELATED
TO HISTORICAL EVENTS.

